onLineSrc.orDesc: Access to Milwaukee County GIS data

dataIdInfo.idAbs: This data represents addresses for Milwaukee County, Wisconsin in 2019. [Points representing locations of addresses - points are placed within the parcel with which an address is associated - when possible, points are placed within the footprint of the building with which an address is associated - when a parcel or building is associated with multiple addresses, multiple points will be placed within each parcel or building. - relates to addressable buildings on BUILDING_ID, parcels on TAXKEY, and street centerlines on CLINE_ID.]
dataIdInfo.idPurp: This data is intended for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
